==Honours and awards== * "[[Gold Star]]" [[Hero of the Soviet Union]], twice (1976, 1980) * Two [[Orders of Lenin]] (1976, 1980) * [[Medal "For Merit in Space Exploration"]] (12 April 2011) - for the great achievements in the field of research, development and utilization of outer space, many years of diligent work, public activities * [[Medal "Veteran of Labour"]] * Gold medal "For services to science and humanity" (Czechoslovakia) * [[Order of Karl Marx]] (East Germany, 13 October 1976) * [[Pilot-Cosmonaut of the USSR]] * Honoured Master of Sports * Honorary Citizen of [[Ryazan]]
